reviewText: This tape is great, Belinda sings great versions of Mad about you, I get weak ,Heaven on Earth, and Vacation. She also sings some other great Go Gos songs as well as other songs from the Heaven on Earth. This tape has good sound and some neat special effects, Its a must have for Belinda Carlisle fans, its the best live concert you can get of Belinda Carlisle, you won't be sorry if you buy this tape.
